com.camerontec.catalys.server.compliance

Interface IClientEntityMapper

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultClientEntityMapper, DummyMarketDataService.Mapper

    public interface IClientEntityMapper
    IClientEntityMapper is an interface to be implemented when it is required to execute certain rules against sub-client entities. The specific implementation should return an Object whose equals() and hashCode() methods are well-behaved. If it is necessary to use a mix of mappings for various FIX sessions, it is essential that equals() is thoughtfully coded to not return true if two different entities are being compared.
    Author:
    Tom Vasak
